name: Janey's Place
tagline: Temporary landing page for future site
body:
### Welcome to the future home of Janey's Place website.
[Janey's place](https://www.facebook.com/Janey0817/) is going to be a home and refuge for dogs. The end goal is to provide a fun and loving atmosphere for dogs. Services that will be provided are doggy daycare, shelter for lost/homeless dogs, and boarding services.
